            <p>
                <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>va<supplied reason="lost">sti</supplied> <unclear>śa</unclear>ka-varṣ<unclear>ātī</unclear>ta <num value="779"><unclear>77</unclear><supplied reason="lost">9</supplied></num> <supplied reason="lost">māsa bhadravā</supplied>da E<supplied reason="lost">kā</supplied>daśa śukla<lb 
                n="2" break="no"/>-pakṣa panirvan· vagai śukra tatkăla ra bavaṁ Anakvi manu<lb 
                n="3" break="no"/>suka sīma savaḥ tampaḥ 4 pavaiḥ rakai vakka pu manota 
                <lb n="4"/>savahani vihāra Abhayānanda
            </p>
